                'text_en' => 'As you know, the President of Turkmenistan recently visited the Kingdom of Bahrain. Within the framework of the visit, Serdar Berdimuhamedov visited the "Safiriyya" Palace in Manama, where he and the King of Bahrain, Hamad bin Isa Al Khalifa, watched an exhibition of thoroughbred Arabian horses, as well as other thoroughbred horses.

