                'text_en' => 'Recently, the Embassy of Turkmenistan in the Republic of Belarus held a briefing on the topic "Achievements in the transport system of Turkmenistan and the new administrative center of the Ahal province - the new city of Arkadag". Teachers and students of the Belarusian State Aviation Academy were invited to this briefing.

